name: MagicLand
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Magicland is an emerging sustainable decentralized one-stop DeFI portal that starts with yield farming powered on Arbitrium and IoTeX. Our focus is to provide a safe yield farming experience for our citizens who are supporting Magicland along the journey to become the most magical DeFI place on Arbitrum and IoTeX.
